downloadTitle: Microsoft OneLake file explorer for Windows
downloadDescription: The OneLake file explorer application seamlessly integrates Microsoft OneLake, the data lake for Microsoft Fabric, with the Windows File Explorer.
detailsSection:
This application automatically syncs all Microsoft OneLake items that you have access to in Windows File Explorer. See more information on OneLake file explorer here
For information about this release, see release notes for OneLake file explorer.
systemRequirementsSection:
Supported Operating Systems: Windows 10 version 1709 and above, Windows 11.
Microsoft Fabric OneLake file explorer is supported on 64-bit (x64) platform.
installInstructionSection:
Download OneLake file explorer MSIX and run the installer.
